---
<section class="relative pt-24 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
	<!-- Grid Pattern Background -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40 -z-10" style="background-image: radial-gradient(#CBD5E1 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 24px 24px;"></div>

	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
		<!-- Live Indicator Badge -->
		<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 mb-8">
			<span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
				<span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-blue-400 opacity-75"></span>
				<span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-blue-500"></span>
			</span>
			<span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#0061FF] uppercase tracking-wider">Ciberseguridad Empresarial de Alto Nivel</span>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Headline -->
		<h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-[#0F172A] leading-tight tracking-tight mb-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto font-sans">
			Servicios de <span class="text-[#0061FF]">Ciberseguridad Avanzada</span>: Protección Proactiva para tu Negocio
		</h1>

		<!-- Subheadline -->
		<p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-sans">
			Anticípate a las amenazas digitales con una estrategia integral de defensa. Protegemos tus activos críticos, garantizamos el cumplimiento normativo y blindamos tus operaciones 24/7.
		</p>

		<!-- CTA Buttons -->
		<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
			<a
				href="#contacto"
				class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-[#0061FF] text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-700 shadow-xl shadow-blue-200 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2 font-sans"
			>
				Consultoría Gratuita
				<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
				</svg>
			</a>
			<a
				href="#servicios"
				class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-white text-slate-700 border border-slate-200 font-bold text-lg rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all font-sans"
			>
				Ver Capacidades
			</a>
		</div>

		<!-- Certifications -->
		<div class="pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
			<p class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 font-sans">Certificaciones y Estándares Globales</p>
			<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-50 grayscale">
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0061FF]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-2 16l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z"/>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-bold font-sans">ISO 27001</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0061FF]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M14 2H6c-1.1 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L4 20c0 1.1.89 2 1.99 2H18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V8l-6-6zm2 16H8v-2h8v2zm0-4H8v-2h8v2zm-3-5V3.5L18.5 9H13z"/>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-bold font-sans">GDPR Cumplimiento</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0061FF]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4z"/>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-bold font-sans">SOC2 TYPE II</span>
				</div>
				<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#0061FF]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path d="M18 8h-1V6c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5S7 3.24 7 6v2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6 9c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2s.9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2-.9 2-2 2zm3.1-9H8.9V6c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1 1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1v2z"/>
					</svg>
					<span class="font-bold font-sans">PCI-DSS</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
